  ('Smoking is the single most modifiable cardiovascular risk factor. Cigarette smoking doubles the risk of coronary heart disease. Within 1 year of smoking cessation, excess coronary artery disease risk is halved. Within 5–15 years, CVD risk approaches that of a lifetime non-smoker. Smoking cessation programs (NRT + behavioural support) should be offered to all current smokers.', '[0,0.4609375,0.3125,-0.5078125,0,-0.1171875,0.265625,0.625,0.0078125,-0.765625,0.5546875,0,0.0078125,-0.59375,0.0859375,-0.328125,0.3125,0.0078125,-0.15625,-0.015625,0.0390625,-0.1484375,-0.3984375,-0.5703125,-0.4296875,0.2109375,0.03125,0.515625,0.0703125,-0.1875,-0.234375,0.203125,0.4921875,0.046875,0.0078125,-0.1484375,0.078125,-0.09375,-0.15625,0.203125,0.0546875,0.40625,-0.078125,-0.0078125,-0.0078125,-0.515625,0.2421875,-0.234375,0.2265625,-0.0703125,0.203125,0.1796875,0.46875,0.1953125,0.1640625,-0.3203125,0.4140625,-0.1875,0.0390625,-0.53125,0.0390625,0.1640625,-0.0390625,-0.3515625,0.375,0.5234375,-0.078125,-0.0390625,0.21875,-0.4609375,-0.3515625,0.4609375,-0.125,0.0234375,-0.078125,0.65625,-0.2734375,0.125,-0.3515625,0.390625,-0.5078125,0.21875,0.2421875,0.8359375,0.0625,0.0390625,-0.15625,0.359375,0.1484375,-0.3203125,-0.3984375,-0.2890625,-0.1328125,-0.375,-0.125,0.171875,-0.296875,-0.3203125,0.5390625,-0.0078125,0.1015625,-0.46875,-0.453125,-0.390625,-0.1171875,-0.4140625,-0.28125,-0.078125,-0.2265625,-0.453125,-0.140625,0.0234375,-0.453125,-0.5234375,0.34375,0.03125,0.1796875,-0.1875,-0.0625,0.0078125,-0.1484375,0.1171875,-0.1640625,-0.015625,-0.21875,0,-0.2734375,0.640625,-0.28125,0.09375,-0.6796875,0.2734375,-0.0078125,-0.0859375,-0.1953125,0.46875,-0.3046875,0.1484375,-0.2109375,0.2265625,0.15625,-0.1875,-0.4296875,0.421875,-0.078125,-0.3515625,0.234375,-0.140625,-0.3203125,-0.140625,0.125,0.421875,-0.421875,0.265625,-0.1875,0.4140625,0.0546875,-0.0546875,-0.2578125,-0.421875,-0.3671875,-0.21875,-0.703125,-0.6171875,0.5078125,0.15625,0.046875,-0.25,0.3046875,0.5078125,-0