  ('Lipoprotein(a) [Lp(a)] is a genetically determined, independent risk factor for atherosclerotic cardiovascular disease. Elevated Lp(a) > 75 nmol/L doubles ASCVD risk. Unlike LDL, Lp(a) is not substantially reduced by statins. It should be measured once in all adults, particularly those with family history of premature CVD or statin-treated patients not achieving LDL targets. Source: ACC/AHA 2019.', '[0,0.078125,-0.359375,-0.53125,0,-0.25,-0.09375,0.828125,-0.0625,-0.8984375,0.25,0.421875,-0.28125,0.03125,0.453125,-0.2109375,0.7734375,0.0625,-0.375,-0.03125,-0.0234375,-0.28125,-0.6484375,0.1640625,-0.9296875,0.6640625,-0.125,-0.4765625,-0.2109375,0.171875,-0.25,-0.078125,-0.09375,0.453125,-0.09375,0.4375,-0.4296875,-0.109375,-0.234375,0.203125,0.1953125,0.3359375,-0.09375,0.1484375,-0.5703125,0.171875,0.09375,-0.3828125,0.4453125,-0.25,-0.0703125,-0.15625,0.5234375,0.109375,-0.46875,-0.1640625,0.7890625,-0.46875,-0.015625,-0.4140625,-0.09375,0.09375,-0.140625,0.5625,0.0390625,0.390625,0.1953125,-0.46875,-0.3515625,0.234375,-0.4453125,0.234375,-0.5625,0.6015625,-0.078125,0.5234375,0.0859375,0.2421875,-0.40625,-0.328125,-0.3203125,-0.1953125,0.046875,0.9296875,0.34375,0.296875,0.53125,0.2109375,-0.578125,-0.7109375,-0.046875,0.5390625,0.0390625,-0.2421875,-0.078125,0.3125,0.515625,-0.359375,0.5625,0.0390625,0.1875,-0.296875,0.1953125,-0.1640625,0.3515625,-0.328125,0.1015625,0.1015625,-0.078125,0.2890625,0.3359375,0.3359375,-0.53125,0.0625,0.4140625,0.25,0.3203125,-0.640625,-0.5234375,-0.3203125,-0.1015625,0.265625,-0.1875,0.03125,-0.4609375,0.234375,0.078125,0.296875,-0.3828125,0.265625,-0.546875,-0.171875,0.4765625,0.140625,-0.03125,0.1484375,-0.1796875,-0.0234375,-0.2734375,0.0546875,0,-0.1015625,-0.09375,0.1875,0.2578125,-0.6171875,0.375,0.0234375,0.1328125,0.09375,0.296875,-0.0703125,-0.203125,0.1171875,0.5703125,-0.0859375,0.0546875,-0.078125,-0.1328125,0.03125,-0.0546875,-0.140625,-0.75,-0.5546875,0.390625,0.0390625,0.171875,0.21875,-0.140625,0.0234375,-0.367