  ('WHO 2011 diagnostic criteria for type 2 diabetes: HbA1c ≥ 53 mmol/mol (7.0%) on two occasions; fasting plasma glucose ≥ 7.0 mmol/L; or 2-hour glucose ≥ 11.1 mmol/L on 75g OGTT. Impaired fasting glucose (IFG): fasting glucose 6.1–6.9 mmol/L. Impaired glucose tolerance (IGT): 2-hour glucose 7.8–11.0 mmol/L. HbA1c 48–52 mmol/mol represents borderline/pre-diabetes range in some Australian guidelines.', '[0,-0.546875,0.2109375,-0.015625,0,0.1171875,0.53125,0.59375,0.0859375,-0.9921875,0.234375,0.1875,0.0546875,0.1953125,0.390625,0.046875,0.2421875,-0.0390625,0.0859375,-0.015625,-0.1484375,0.3125,-0.7890625,-0.5390625,-0.875,0.4375,-0.2421875,0.484375,-0.2578125,0.5625,-0.2734375,0.4140625,-0.0546875,-0.2734375,-0.1875,-0.1875,-0.0390625,0.296875,-0.5234375,0.109375,0,-0.015625,-0.0859375,0.2109375,0.2265625,0.3046875,-0.03125,-0.3125,0.140625,-0.453125,0.1015625,-0.2265625,-0.09375,0.21875,0.4609375,0.109375,0.359375,0.421875,-0.6953125,-0.6015625,-0.0546875,0.0703125,-0.0625,0.1796875,-0.046875,-0.0859375,-0.1484375,0.3046875,-0.2734375,0.390625,-0.5546875,0.53125,0.140625,0.203125,0.234375,0.0703125,-0.234375,-0.375,-0.34375,0.03125,0.0078125,0.2734375,0.5234375,0.671875,0.1796875,-0.53125,0.3984375,0.359375,-0.5390625,-0.6015625,-0.328125,0.2734375,-0.0078125,-0.171875,0.453125,0.1640625,-0.3828125,0.1796875,-0.0390625,-0.296875,-0.34375,-0.15625,0.5546875,0.4765625,0.59375,-0.40625,0.6640625,0.5625,-0.234375,-0.3828125,-0.59375,-0.2734375,0.2578125,-0.421875,0.359375,-0.1484375,0.6171875,-0.53125,-0.4921875,-0.0625,-0.078125,-0.265625,0.0546875,-0.0703125,-0.265625,0.40625,0.3515625,0.59375,0.125,0.1953125,-0.6484375,-0.0390625,0.2578125,-0.25,-0.25,0.0859375,0.0546875,-0.109375,-0.0234375,0.078125,0.1484375,-0.15625,-0.21875,-0.484375,0.0859375,0.1328125,0.5,-0.109375,-0.0546875,-0.5,0.1015625,0.2109375,0.1875,-0.140625,-0.4296875,-0.078125,0.171875,0.34375,0.1328125,-0.15625,-0.203125,0.15625,0.0078125,-0.4375,-0.0390625,0.1328125,0.0546875,-0.2109375,0,0.42968