  ('Visceral (central) adiposity — measured by waist circumference — is a stronger predictor of metabolic risk than BMI alone. Waist circumference > 94 cm in men and > 80 cm in women (IDF European thresholds) significantly elevates risk of insulin resistance, T2DM, and CVD. Visceral fat secretes pro-inflammatory adipokines including TNF-α, IL-6, and leptin that directly impair insulin signalling.', '[0,0.1328125,-0.3046875,-0.5078125,0,0.1875,-0.21875,0.8515625,0.109375,-0.9921875,0.03125,0.484375,-0.0078125,0.125,0.640625,0.125,0.3359375,0.15625,-0.03125,0.03125,0.0234375,0.203125,-0.6640625,-0.5078125,-0.890625,0.5,-0.0859375,-0.1171875,-0.0859375,0.4375,0.125,0.421875,0.421875,0.171875,0.015625,0.2109375,-0.203125,0.15625,-0.5390625,0.25,0.0078125,0.46875,0.3671875,-0.1328125,-0.203125,-0.7265625,0.2578125,0.0078125,-0.375,0.2578125,0.0390625,0.078125,0.46875,0.1796875,0.28125,0.1875,0.375,0.078125,0.109375,-0.5546875,0.2890625,0.7734375,-0.1640625,0.2421875,0.203125,-0.015625,0.3203125,0.4375,0.125,-0.171875,0,0.5390625,0.203125,-0.0390625,0.125,0.484375,-0.1171875,0.046875,-0.640625,0.359375,-0.15625,-0.1796875,0.28125,0.921875,-0.125,0.09375,0.2109375,-0.15625,-0.515625,-0.296875,-0.2734375,0.09375,-0.3359375,-0.40625,0.109375,-0.1015625,-0.6796875,0,0.6640625,-0.1484375,-0.2265625,-0.4296875,-0.1484375,0.03125,0.703125,-0.109375,0.484375,0.171875,0.2421875,-0.171875,0.203125,-0.53125,0.0703125,-0.078125,0.0703125,-0.453125,0.3046875,-0.6484375,-0.2421875,-0.5,-0.0703125,0.0390625,-0.2265625,0.328125,0.2734375,-0.046875,0.09375,0.0078125,-0.453125,0.0078125,-0.8828125,0.3671875,-0.0625,0.0234375,0.109375,-0.1640625,0.1796875,-0.1328125,-0.1015625,0.3046875,-0.03125,0.015625,0.046875,-0.0078125,0.015625,-0.234375,-0.1015625,-0.265625,-0.4609375,-0.1484375,0.1875,0.2421875,0.203125,-0.125,-0.375,0.3515625,-0.015625,0.515625,-0.09375,0.265625,0.0703125,0.0859375,-0.4140625,-0.2734375,0,-0.046875,-0.0234375,0.1015625,0.4375,0.375,-0.3203125,0.1640625,0.3515625,-0.