  ('Hypertension in midlife (ages 40–65) independently doubles the risk of dementia later in life. Treating hypertension to < 130/80 mmHg in midlife is one of the most evidence-based dementia prevention strategies. The SPRINT-MIND trial demonstrated that intensive blood pressure lowering (SBP target < 120 mmHg) significantly reduced mild cognitive impairment risk compared to standard control (< 140 mmHg).', '[0,0.140625,-0.3203125,-0.203125,0,-0.265625,0.1015625,0.5234375,0.0546875,-0.9296875,0.1640625,0.4609375,0.0546875,-0.1640625,-0.2109375,0.1640625,-0.5625,-0.09375,0.1796875,-0.015625,-0.1015625,-0.0078125,0.234375,-0.328125,-0.4921875,-0.21875,-0.171875,-0.1953125,0.1484375,0.3671875,-0.4921875,0.09375,-0.1484375,0.2734375,-0.0390625,0.1015625,0.0078125,-0.09375,-0.4375,0.125,-0.6328125,0.3125,0,0.359375,-0.40625,0.125,0.1875,-0.5,0.15625,-0.1484375,-0.359375,-0.2265625,-0.296875,0.2890625,0.359375,0.15625,0.359375,0.078125,0.5703125,-0.25,0.1640625,0.328125,0.5703125,0.1171875,-0.078125,-0.0078125,0.09375,-0.859375,0,-0.03125,-0.2578125,-0.1015625,-0.3046875,-0.375,0.3828125,0.15625,0.109375,-0.0703125,-0.5,-0.171875,-0.7421875,-0.0859375,0.2265625,0.8203125,0.21875,0.1015625,0.1171875,-0.0390625,0.34375,0.1328125,0.2734375,-0.3203125,-0.171875,-0.4453125,0.65625,0.3828125,0.1875,-0.4609375,0.3515625,-0.3359375,-0.0078125,0.171875,0.09375,0.6328125,0.71875,-0.0078125,0.5,0.234375,-0.3984375,0.3359375,-0.359375,-0.1171875,0,-0.40625,0.3828125,0.296875,0.4375,-0.3203125,-0.2109375,-0.171875,-0.046875,-0.1328125,-0.0546875,0.0703125,-0.2109375,0.171875,-0.0390625,0.4296875,-0.234375,-0.1640625,-0.8984375,0.3984375,0.5,0.1328125,0,-0.359375,0.1015625,0.3515625,-0.1640625,0.09375,0.0703125,-0.09375,-0.2734375,-0.1171875,-0.1640625,-0.2109375,0.0546875,-0.359375,0.1953125,-0.03125,-0.21875,0.25,-0.265625,-0.171875,-0.0390625,0,-0.2265625,-0.0390625,0.09375,-0.15625,0.0234375,-0.03125,-0.234375,-0.546875,0.1796875,0.109375,-0.46875,0.1640625,0.03125,0.390625,-0.2578