  ('Physical inactivity is a modifiable dementia risk factor, accounting for ~2% PAR in the Lancet Commission 2024. Regular aerobic exercise (≥ 150 minutes/week of moderate-intensity) increases BDNF (brain-derived neurotrophic factor), promotes neurogenesis in the hippocampus, and improves cerebrovascular perfusion. Exercise is associated with 35% lower risk of cognitive decline in observational studies.', '[0,0.234375,-0.5078125,-0.3828125,0,-0.234375,0.1484375,0.3046875,0.046875,-0.9453125,0.09375,0.15625,0.1171875,-0.2265625,0.2890625,-0.5859375,0.078125,0.0703125,-0.1875,-0.03125,-0.0078125,0.1640625,-0.203125,-0.2265625,-0.7265625,0.1875,-0.1640625,0.078125,-0.1171875,0.1875,-0.3984375,0.0625,0.1875,0.078125,-0.109375,0.6328125,0.109375,0.1796875,-0.3359375,0.21875,-0.3828125,0.3984375,0.15625,0.390625,-0.328125,-0.3828125,0.296875,-0.2421875,0.234375,-0.234375,0.046875,-0.2734375,-0.359375,0.03125,-0.203125,-0.015625,0.015625,-0.203125,0.0234375,-0.046875,0.0234375,-0.0859375,0.453125,0.1640625,0,0.4609375,0.2734375,-0.7265625,0.421875,0.1953125,-0.2421875,0.484375,0.078125,-0.3359375,0,0.203125,0.0625,-0.234375,-0.4921875,0.1875,-0.0859375,-0.546875,0.03125,0.8671875,-0.109375,0.046875,-0.078125,-0.1796875,-0.28125,0.0859375,0.015625,-0.25,0.078125,-0.203125,0.0625,0.2109375,0.328125,-0.1640625,0.34375,-0.0859375,0.1171875,-0.0390625,0.34375,0.015625,0.4296875,0.0703125,-0.1015625,0.0859375,-0.484375,0.2265625,-0.078125,0.1640625,0.0234375,0.3359375,0.046875,-0.21875,0.4453125,-0.171875,-0.046875,-0.265625,-0.0703125,0.1015625,-0.1640625,-0.03125,-0.328125,-0.375,0.0859375,0.4453125,-0.21875,0.0390625,-0.3984375,0.2265625,0.484375,-0.0859375,-0.2109375,-0.25,-0.21875,0.0703125,-0.2734375,-0.25,0.0625,0.1484375,-0.1875,0.0625,-0.2109375,-0.3359375,0.40625,-0.296875,0.0546875,-0.28125,0,-0.0625,-0.078125,-0.078125,-0.03125,0.328125,-0.0859375,0.109375,-0.1796875,0.09375,0,-0.15625,-0.0703125,-0.6328125,0.296875,-0.0625,0.0703125,-0.1875,-0.15625,0.125,-0.171875