  ('Sleep quality has a direct impact on amyloid-beta clearance from the brain via the glymphatic system. The glymphatic system is most active during slow-wave sleep, clearing amyloid and tau proteins that accumulate during waking hours. Chronic sleep < 6 hours or > 9 hours is associated with higher amyloid burden on PET imaging and increased dementia risk. Sleep optimisation is a cost-free dementia prevention strategy.', '[0,0.3125,-0.1484375,-0.625,0,-0.15625,-0.4296875,0.671875,0.078125,-0.9609375,-0.0625,0.390625,0.1328125,-0.078125,0.5859375,0.2109375,-0.375,-0.0859375,0.265625,-0.0859375,-0.03125,-0.03125,-0.09375,-0.515625,-0.53125,-0.375,-0.1015625,0.1640625,0.5234375,0.234375,-0.3828125,0.0390625,0.15625,0.5546875,-0.0703125,0.171875,-0.140625,-0.2421875,-0.3046875,0.5234375,0,0.25,-0.1484375,0.0546875,0.046875,-0.0390625,0.421875,0.3359375,0.4140625,-0.0390625,-0.40625,-0.3828125,0.296875,0.265625,0.0390625,0.3359375,0.1484375,0.0390625,0.0390625,0.2578125,0.2734375,-0.234375,0.4375,0.40625,0.0703125,0.4609375,0.0625,-0.703125,-0.0625,0.28125,0.2109375,0.0625,0.140625,-0.0234375,0.3828125,-0.0703125,0.21875,-0.03125,-0.5703125,-0.34375,-0.0859375,-0.0546875,0.4921875,0.6953125,0.1328125,-0.03125,-0.1953125,0.0625,-0.234375,-0.140625,-0.140625,-0.4453125,-0.2109375,-0.109375,0.359375,0.5703125,0.296875,-0.5390625,0.0234375,-0.2421875,-0.0703125,-0.1015625,0.2421875,0.40625,0.6875,0.1640625,0.3046875,-0.0859375,-0.171875,0.546875,-0.125,0.609375,-0.3125,0.40625,0.2109375,0.234375,0.734375,-0.296875,0.0625,0.0546875,0.125,0.5,0.234375,-0.34375,-0.1328125,-0.7734375,0.265625,0.390625,-0.109375,0.0859375,-0.7421875,0.15625,0.015625,-0.1953125,-0.15625,-0.4921875,0.1484375,0.1640625,0.1640625,0.421875,-0.375,0.078125,-0.1796875,-0.40625,-0.09375,-0.1640625,0.1875,-0.046875,-0.1328125,-0.03125,-0.078125,0.15625,0.1015625,-0.1796875,0.1640625,0.109375,-0.28125,0.140625,0.0625,-0.28125,-0.40625,-0.0703125,0.1953125,-0.6328125,0.2421875,0.234375,-0.40625,-0.0703125,