  ('High LDL cholesterol (> 3.0 mmol/L) in midlife is a newly identified modifiable dementia risk factor in the 2024 Lancet Commission. Elevated LDL promotes cerebral small vessel disease, vascular dementia, and potentially amyloid-beta production. Statin therapy for LDL reduction in midlife may reduce vascular dementia risk. LDL control is now part of comprehensive dementia prevention alongside cardiovascular prevention.', '[0,-0.015625,-0.453125,-0.1171875,0,-0.1171875,0.1875,0.75,0.125,-0.953125,0.234375,0.2109375,-0.125,-0.234375,-0.09375,-0.046875,-0.1875,-0.2578125,-0.390625,-0.0625,-0.109375,-0.125,-0.0625,0.125,-0.6875,-0.203125,-0.125,0.109375,0.5078125,0.5703125,-0.359375,0.015625,0.65625,-0.0625,-0.0625,0.171875,-0.2578125,-0.2421875,-0.5,0.3828125,-0.0703125,0.2890625,0.15625,0.2265625,-0.5625,-0.1640625,-0.0546875,-0.5703125,-0.421875,-0.1015625,-0.234375,-0.25,0.046875,0.0546875,0.078125,0.015625,0.765625,0.1328125,0.234375,-0.3125,-0.09375,0.328125,0.4921875,0.4453125,-0.15625,0.40625,0.2109375,-0.671875,-0.0625,0.1796875,-0.6953125,0.1328125,-0.1640625,0.140625,0.2734375,0.328125,0.0546875,0.1953125,-0.28125,0.0703125,-0.4453125,-0.2890625,-0.1484375,0.8984375,-0.0234375,-0.21875,0.109375,0.015625,-0.515625,-0.6484375,-0.1796875,0.1328125,0.0625,-0.5234375,0.1484375,0.203125,0.5390625,-0.5625,0.8046875,-0.1875,0.0078125,0.078125,0.140625,0.3125,0.5546875,-0.4765625,0.1328125,-0.0390625,-0.0390625,0.5390625,-0.3984375,0,-0.4140625,0.1640625,0.46875,0.3203125,0.0703125,-0.0625,-0.1484375,-0.0078125,-0.171875,0.21875,-0.1328125,0.0078125,-0.1328125,-0.2421875,0.3515625,0.296875,-0.046875,-0.15625,-0.75,0.25,0.328125,0.1484375,-0.4140625,-0.1484375,-0.109375,0.1953125,-0.1015625,0.2421875,0.1015625,0.09375,-0.1328125,-0.1953125,-0.3984375,-0.484375,0.4140625,-0.3828125,0.1015625,0.140625,0.109375,0.265625,-0.0859375,0.0625,-0.03125,0.0859375,-0.1171875,-0.0546875,-0.0859375,-0.03125,-0.3046875,-0.03125,-0.671875,-0.515625,0.4453125,0.0390625,0.0078125,-0