  ('Tobacco is the leading preventable cause of cancer globally, responsible for approximately 15% of all new cancer cases (IARC 2024). Smoking causes cancers of the lung, mouth, throat, oesophagus, stomach, pancreas, kidney, bladder, cervix, and bone marrow (AML). Risk of lung cancer begins declining within 5 years of smoking cessation. After 10 years of cessation, lung cancer risk is halved compared to continuing smokers.', '[0,0.203125,-0.234375,-0.3828125,0,0.46875,0.171875,0.09375,0.078125,-0.890625,0.515625,0.0234375,0.015625,-0.734375,0.2265625,-0.3359375,-0.046875,-0.203125,-0.578125,0,0.015625,-0.2265625,-0.734375,-0.6484375,0.203125,0.71875,0.1328125,0.9140625,-0.328125,-0.328125,-0.140625,0.0390625,0.4296875,0.3203125,-0.1484375,-0.4453125,0.0859375,0.0078125,-0.546875,0.3125,-0.4296875,-0.1796875,-0.3984375,-0.2734375,0.2421875,-0.890625,0.234375,-0.5625,-0.234375,0.2890625,0.15625,-0.25,0.65625,0.1953125,0.3828125,-0.328125,0.7734375,0.2265625,-0.4140625,-0.6328125,-0.515625,-0.1328125,0.5390625,-0.328125,0.296875,0.109375,-0.1484375,0.078125,-0.4140625,-0.2890625,-0.4453125,-0.375,-0.7265625,-0.015625,0.28125,0.6484375,-0.2890625,0.171875,-0.2734375,0.171875,-0.609375,0.4921875,-0.1875,0.796875,0.015625,-0.5625,-0.3828125,0.015625,0.453125,-0.203125,-0.7578125,-0.125,0.4453125,-0.953125,0.109375,0.453125,-0.078125,0.3828125,0.203125,0.1640625,-0.078125,-0.5625,-0.1796875,-0.4453125,0.0234375,-0.421875,-0.3046875,0.390625,0,-0.671875,0,0.578125,-0.78125,0.171875,0.3515625,-0.40625,-0.3984375,0.25,-0.59375,-0.8671875,-0.0859375,0.234375,-0.1953125,0.5234375,0.4375,-0.5703125,-0.578125,0.3515625,0.4140625,0.1484375,-0.5078125,0.1015625,-0.59375,-0.3671875,-0.1015625,-0.03125,0.1484375,0.1328125,-0.34375,-0.1640625,0.15625,-0.265625,-0.2734375,0.3125,-0.4140625,-0.6796875,-0.0234375,0.5546875,-0.4609375,0.0234375,0.2265625,0.3359375,-0.21875,0.3515625,0.296875,-0.125,-0.15625,0.125,-0.3046875,-0.4609375,-0.1953125,-0.3203125,-0.5390625,-0.71875,0.3046875,0