  ('Excess body weight (overweight BMI 25–29.9 and obese BMI ≥ 30) is linked to 13 cancer types by IARC: breast (post-menopausal), colorectal, endometrial, oesophageal (adenocarcinoma), gallbladder, kidney, liver, ovarian, pancreatic, stomach (cardia), thyroid, multiple myeloma, and meningioma. Mechanisms include elevated oestrogen, insulin, IGF-1, and chronic inflammation. Achieving and maintaining healthy BMI 18.5–24.9 significantly reduces cancer risk.', '[0,0.125,-0.4296875,-0.6015625,0,0.5859375,-0.625,0.4296875,0.125,-0.9375,-0.09375,-0.078125,0.265625,-0.234375,0.1328125,-0.0625,0.546875,-0.5078125,0.1171875,0.015625,-0.0078125,-0.015625,-0.3984375,-0.40625,-0.5859375,0.609375,-0.015625,0.6484375,-0.375,0.21875,0.328125,-0.0703125,0.4765625,0.09375,-0.1953125,-0.4609375,-0.046875,0.03125,-0.703125,-0.09375,0.078125,-0.0546875,0.296875,-0.3515625,0.3671875,-0.6484375,0.3203125,-0.359375,-0.2265625,0.4921875,0.28125,0.0625,-0.3984375,0.1875,0.28125,0.1328125,0.734375,0.1171875,-0.078125,0.109375,0.1484375,0.1328125,-0.1328125,0.265625,0.1875,-0.2421875,0.1015625,0.5078125,-0.53125,0.4140625,-0.671875,0.421875,-0.015625,-0.21875,0.6953125,0.40625,-0.0546875,0.3515625,-0.6015625,0.1796875,-0.578125,-0.5546875,-0.109375,0.796875,-0.203125,-0.5859375,-0.59375,-0.328125,0.3828125,-0.1953125,0.0234375,-0.0234375,-0.1796875,-0.578125,0.4375,-0.046875,-0.4375,0.109375,0.5703125,0.109375,0.015625,0.140625,0.265625,-0.1328125,0.2734375,-0.1328125,0.2421875,0.1015625,-0.40625,-0.1640625,-0.1953125,-0.2890625,-0.171875,0.421875,-0.4375,-0.5703125,-0.125,-0.1640625,-0.5,-0.703125,0.171875,-0.109375,-0.0234375,0.4140625,0.3046875,-0.109375,-0.2890625,0.09375,-0.046875,-0.1953125,-0.28125,0.2109375,-0.578125,-0.3203125,0.1640625,0.078125,0.4609375,0.0546875,0.09375,0,0.3671875,-0.0625,-0.1640625,0.40625,-0.09375,-0.34375,-0.078125,0.140625,-0.046875,-0.1484375,0.421875,0.390625,0.0859375,0.046875,0.0078125,0.5703125,0.375,-0.1015625,-0.359375,0.0390625,-0.21875,-0.0390625,-0.