  ('Physical inactivity is associated with increased risk of colon cancer (40–50% risk reduction with regular activity), breast cancer (20–30% reduction), and endometrial cancer (30–40% reduction). The Cancer Council Australia recommends ≥ 150 minutes of moderate-intensity physical activity per week for cancer risk reduction. Exercise reduces cancer risk through multiple mechanisms including insulin/IGF-1 regulation, immune function, prostaglandin levels, and reduced obesity.', '[0,0.46875,-0.1640625,-0.546875,0,0.3828125,-0.0703125,0.296875,-0.0078125,-0.9921875,0.2265625,-0.3671875,0.2109375,0.03125,0.078125,-0.734375,0.609375,0.0390625,-0.5625,0,0.09375,-0.1953125,-0.3359375,-0.8203125,-0.75,0.7265625,0.046875,0.5,-0.53125,0.25,-0.234375,-0.2890625,0.375,0.015625,-0.03125,0.0546875,-0.0703125,0.265625,-0.34375,0.1875,-0.4609375,0.078125,0.078125,0.265625,-0.3828125,-0.8125,0.0625,-0.375,0.1171875,0.0078125,0.3515625,-0.265625,-0.453125,0.203125,0.5390625,0.0390625,0.1875,-0.0390625,-0.3125,0.0546875,-0.390625,-0.0625,0.375,0.015625,0.2109375,-0.109375,-0.0390625,-0.015625,0.0078125,0.4296875,-0.359375,0.390625,-0.03125,-0.5703125,0.453125,0.6015625,-0.046875,0.2109375,-0.4453125,0.2421875,-0.40625,-0.5859375,-0.453125,0.9375,0.0546875,0.140625,-0.2578125,0.0859375,0.0390625,0.2890625,0.046875,-0.21875,-0.0078125,-0.5234375,-0.0859375,-0.328125,-0.375,-0.078125,0.3203125,0,-0.046875,-0.2578125,0.0625,-0.3671875,0.125,-0.0703125,-0.5859375,-0.0234375,-0.40625,-0.109375,-0.3828125,-0.21875,0.359375,0.484375,-0.0234375,-0.3671875,0.1640625,-0.1640625,-0.21875,-0.59375,0.0546875,-0.15625,-0.1328125,-0.109375,0.0390625,-0.3203125,-0.046875,0.265625,0.0625,-0.078125,0.0703125,0.03125,-0.1953125,-0.09375,-0.0390625,-0.0390625,0.265625,0.2734375,-0.2890625,-0.3828125,0.296875,-0.0859375,-0.0546875,0.21875,-0.0625,-0.4140625,0.1328125,0.125,-0.140625,-0.4375,0.1015625,0.15625,-0.4296875,-0.0625,-0.1015625,0.453125,0.25,0.2265625,-0.5078125,-0.015625,-0.0625,-0.0390625,-0.5