  ('UV radiation is the primary cause of all skin cancers (basal cell carcinoma, squamous cell carcinoma, and melanoma) in Australia. Australia has the highest melanoma incidence globally. SunSmart guidelines recommend: SPF 50+ sunscreen applied 20 minutes before sun exposure and reapplied every 2 hours; protective clothing, hats, and sunglasses; seeking shade between 10am–3pm (AEDT). Regular full-skin checks by a doctor are recommended annually for high-risk individuals.', '[0,-0.1484375,0.4921875,-0.5546875,0,0.109375,-0.0390625,0.2109375,0.0625,-0.984375,0.109375,-0.484375,0.046875,-0.4140625,0.375,-0.1875,0.046875,0.046875,0.0859375,0.0390625,-0.25,0.375,-0.453125,-0.1953125,-0.265625,-0.234375,-0.0234375,0.59375,0.5546875,0.1015625,-0.40625,0.1328125,0.5,0.34375,-0.21875,-0.1953125,0,0.1328125,0.0234375,-0.0390625,-0.1875,0,-0.1953125,0.1875,0.4453125,-0.40625,0.3515625,0.109375,0.140625,-0.1796875,0.3125,-0.453125,-0.1171875,0.1015625,0.15625,0.1796875,0.453125,0.1953125,0.0625,-0.2890625,-0.2265625,0.328125,0.5703125,-0.0625,0.1953125,-0.171875,-0.2109375,-0.4609375,-0.15625,0.1171875,-0.6015625,0.3125,0.453125,0.109375,0,0.4140625,-0.28125,0.1328125,-0.34375,0.140625,-0.25,0.1015625,0.171875,0.125,-0.1953125,-0.4140625,0.203125,-0.015625,-0.2265625,-0.5,-0.234375,0.453125,-0.1328125,-0.5,0.1796875,0.0078125,-0.2734375,-0.390625,0.15625,-0.28125,-0.3984375,-0.5546875,0.21875,0.0703125,0.0703125,-0.03125,-0.359375,-0.328125,-0.5390625,-0.3125,-0.5234375,-0.1171875,-0.5234375,-0.34375,0.125,-0.2734375,0.3125,-0.46875,-0.3984375,0.1640625,-0.1953125,0.0859375,-0.3359375,0.25,-0.296875,-0.578125,0.390625,0.5,0.0625,-0.09375,0.1484375,-0.2890625,-0.2734375,0.0390625,0.234375,-0.1796875,-0.1328125,0.2109375,-0.1171875,-0.046875,0.046875,-0.140625,-0.03125,0.2734375,0.0546875,0.015625,-0.015625,0.53125,0.234375,0.0546875,-0.09375,0.03125,-0.234375,0.09375,0.046875,0.1796875,-0.1484375,0.3984375,-0.203125,-0.265625,0.0390625,-0.109375,-0.2578125,-0.171875,-0.1171875,