  ('The National Bowel Cancer Screening Program (NBCSP) offers free immunochemical faecal occult blood test (iFOBT) kits to all Australians aged 50–74 years every 2 years. Bowel cancer is Australia''s second most common cancer. When detected early (Stage I), the 5-year survival rate is > 90%. Regular iFOBT screening reduces bowel cancer mortality by approximately 25%. A positive iFOBT requires colonoscopy follow-up.', '[0,0.0078125,-0.0546875,-0.171875,0,0.203125,0.1640625,0.234375,0.0625,-0.90625,0.3125,-0.1796875,0.2109375,-0.0078125,0.2890625,-0.0546875,0.5390625,-0.1328125,-0.28125,-0.0234375,-0.234375,0.125,-0.03125,-0.6875,-0.2890625,0,-0.1484375,0.171875,-0.15625,0.09375,-0.453125,-0.1328125,0.0625,0.4609375,-0.15625,-0.4609375,-0.046875,0.09375,-0.09375,0.0625,-0.3046875,0.109375,-0.296875,-0.0625,0.28125,0.140625,0.1484375,-0.1875,0.1328125,-0.1171875,-0.0390625,-0.09375,-0.3359375,0.2265625,0.15625,-0.265625,0.4140625,0.1171875,0.34375,-0.7421875,-0.1640625,0.3359375,0.1796875,-0.0703125,0.09375,-0.0859375,-0.5390625,-0.3125,-0.28125,0.3125,-0.34375,0.2109375,0.2734375,-0.1171875,0.0234375,-0.2578125,-0.125,0.03125,-0.4453125,-0.1484375,-0.3359375,0.1015625,-0.234375,0.71875,-0.0390625,-0.234375,0.234375,0.2578125,-0.1328125,-0.4140625,-0.2421875,0.234375,-0.15625,-0.296875,0.2421875,-0.2734375,-0.125,-0.2265625,0.359375,-0.3828125,-0.15625,0.375,0.390625,0.1953125,-0.2265625,-0.1953125,0.4375,0.0703125,-0.1953125,-0.265625,-0.40625,-0.375,-0.21875,-0.0390625,-0.2578125,-0.328125,-0.203125,-0.6171875,0.078125,-0.375,0.3125,-0.2421875,-0.0859375,-0.15625,-0.1484375,-0.390625,0.0390625,0,0.078125,0.1640625,-0.3984375,-0.0390625,-0.3046875,0.0546875,-0.2265625,-0.3359375,0,-0.0859375,-0.2109375,0.0234375,0.4375,-0.1015625,-0.1015625,-0.171875,-0.15625,-0.25,0,-0.25,0.09375,-0.125,0.03125,0.15625,-0.2578125,-0.2109375,-0.1484375,0.0703125,0.2265625,0.328125,0.0859375,-0.21875,0.2890625,0.3359375,-0.203125,-0.28125,0.1171875,0.1796875,-0.015625,-0.140625,0.1718