  ('The National Cervical Screening Program (NCSP) replaced the Pap smear in 2017 with a 5-yearly Cervical Screening Test (CST) using HPV DNA testing for women aged 25–74. HPV vaccination (Gardasil 9) has dramatically reduced high-risk HPV prevalence in Australian youth. 99% of cervical cancers are caused by HPV. Regular CST reduces cervical cancer mortality. HPV vaccination does not eliminate the need for continued cervical screening.', '[0,-0.3984375,-0.328125,-0.25,0,0.1171875,0.140625,0.46875,0.109375,-0.859375,0.4296875,-0.0234375,0.0546875,0.0625,0.3828125,0.328125,-0.1796875,-0.125,0.1171875,-0.03125,-0.2890625,0.25,-0.3984375,-0.390625,-0.4453125,-0.2890625,0.0078125,0.4375,-0.1953125,0.078125,-0.4140625,-0.125,0.328125,0.015625,-0.015625,-0.4765625,0.484375,0.1484375,-0.484375,0.2578125,-0.3515625,-0.4296875,-0.0625,0.2578125,-0.3046875,0.265625,0.0859375,-0.015625,-0.1796875,0.015625,0.0078125,-0.046875,-0.140625,0.25,-0.078125,0.09375,0.609375,-0.15625,0.4375,-0.7421875,-0.140625,0.171875,-0.296875,-0.125,0.1015625,0.40625,-0.234375,-0.625,-0.375,-0.2734375,-0.3359375,0.1953125,-0.203125,-0.40625,0.1171875,-0.0625,-0.015625,0.171875,-0.40625,0.0703125,-0.34375,-0.015625,0.03125,0.8203125,0.21875,-0.2421875,-0.0625,0.4765625,0.1484375,-0.34375,-0.0546875,0.3984375,-0.203125,-0.515625,0.28125,0.03125,-0.328125,-0.3671875,0.3359375,-0.140625,0.3828125,-0.5078125,-0.09375,-0.0703125,-0.3984375,-0.2265625,0.171875,-0.3359375,-0.2109375,0.0078125,-0.296875,0.0078125,-0.0625,0.21875,0.34375,0.0546875,0.234375,-0.5390625,-0.4765625,-0.359375,-0.25,-0.1328125,-0.1328125,0.0234375,-0.1640625,-0.0390625,0.296875,0.3359375,-0.0234375,0.046875,-0.21875,0.1171875,-0.359375,0.359375,0.09375,0.0390625,-0.1953125,-0.1796875,-0.3203125,-0.0859375,0.015625,0.0078125,-0.4296875,-0.3203125,0.0546875,0.21875,-0.15625,0.2734375,0.1640625,-0.03125,0.2421875,-0.0546875,-0.234375,-0.2421875,0.203125,-0.171875,0.0078125,-0.0546875,0.171875,-0.1953125,-0.2265625,0.1875,-0.46875,-0.7