  ('The 2024 RACGP and Healthy Bones Australia guideline uses FRAX (WHO Fracture Risk Assessment Tool) to estimate 10-year major osteoporotic fracture (MOF) risk. Thresholds: FRAX MOF ≥ 10% → refer for DXA bone mineral density scan; FRAX MOF ≥ 20% and/or hip fracture ≥ 3% → consider pharmacotherapy; FRAX MOF ≥ 30% or hip ≥ 4.5% → very high/imminent fracture risk → treat urgently. FRAX tool: fraxplus.org.', '[0,0.2734375,0.1875,-0.140625,0,0.2265625,0.1953125,-0.0703125,0.0859375,-0.8046875,-0.3046875,0.390625,-0.0859375,-0.1796875,0.3203125,-0.296875,-0.078125,-0.1953125,-0.2734375,-0.03125,-0.078125,-0.0546875,-0.515625,-0.4140625,-0.65625,0.2421875,-0.1015625,-0.5546875,-0.3046875,0.09375,-0.34375,0.1796875,0.09375,-0.2421875,-0.0703125,0.2578125,-0.1171875,-0.0390625,-0.265625,0.4453125,-0.3984375,0.0859375,0.0078125,0.203125,-0.0625,0.2421875,0.1171875,-0.0390625,0.0625,-0.046875,0.0625,0,0.0625,-0.0078125,-0.171875,-0.234375,0.34375,0.1640625,0.3359375,-0.6796875,0.1171875,0.109375,0.1640625,-0.03125,-0.078125,0.1171875,-0.2421875,-0.7265625,-0.09375,0.25,-0.2578125,0.4140625,-0.21875,0.015625,0.2578125,-0.203125,-0.1484375,-0.1640625,-0.6640625,-0.140625,-0.1015625,-0.109375,0.1328125,0.5703125,-0.234375,0.5078125,0.1796875,0.0625,-0.28125,-0.5,0.0234375,-0.125,-0.6171875,-0.234375,-0.1875,0,0.140625,-0.171875,-0.09375,-0.265625,-0.109375,-0.4375,0.140625,0.0546875,0.34375,0.1171875,-0.2109375,0,-0.0859375,0.3828125,-0.4765625,0.0078125,0.015625,-0.0078125,-0.0546875,-0.0703125,0.203125,0.0078125,0.15625,-0.15625,0.21875,-0.390625,-0.2578125,0.0390625,-0.0546875,-0.21875,0.265625,0.0625,-0.0078125,0.0859375,-0.609375,0.0078125,-0.0078125,0.2421875,0.046875,-0.1328125,-0.2421875,0.171875,0.0078125,0.109375,0.0078125,-0.1640625,-0.0390625,0.09375,0.03125,-0.328125,0.390625,-0.265625,0.1953125,-0.171875,0.09375,-0.1015625,-0.15625,-0.0859375,-0.125,0.046875,0.2734375,0.0234375,-0.0859375,-0.09375,0.0390625,-0.0625,-0.5546875,-0.6328125,0.078125,0.0234375,0.257812