  ('Adequate calcium intake is the foundation of bone health. Recommended daily intake: 1,000 mg/day for adults; 1,300 mg/day for adults over 70 and women over 50. Diet-first approach recommended: dairy (yoghurt, cheese, milk), fortified foods, canned fish with bones, tofu. Calcium supplements should only be used when diet is insufficient (< 800 mg/day from food). Calcium carbonate is best absorbed with food; calcium citrate can be taken without food.', '[0,0.4375,0.25,-0.0859375,0,0.1015625,0.34375,0.6171875,-0.015625,-0.9375,-0.890625,0.109375,-0.0859375,0.15625,0.0390625,-0.6953125,-0.046875,-0.140625,0.1171875,0,-0.3828125,-0.3984375,-0.15625,-0.3125,-0.8359375,0.0546875,-0.140625,-0.2265625,0.625,-0.1796875,0.0625,0.15625,0.09375,-0.1484375,0.0078125,0.1171875,0.0234375,-0.1640625,-0.3125,-0.71875,-0.1796875,-0.5859375,-0.375,0.140625,-0.5,-0.0078125,-0.1640625,-0.4296875,0.140625,0.5703125,0.0234375,0.078125,0.1953125,0.3515625,-0.46875,0.375,0.4375,0.2578125,0.0078125,-0.6328125,0.25,-0.234375,0.6640625,-0.4375,0.46875,-0.1015625,-0.5,-0.1328125,-0.3671875,0.4375,-0.5234375,0.703125,-0.2109375,-0.2109375,0.015625,-0.0703125,-0.1640625,0.375,-0.8046875,0.2734375,-0.34375,0.0859375,-0.0078125,0.890625,-0.296875,0.40625,0.375,-0.2421875,0.125,-0.609375,0.0234375,-0.2265625,0.015625,0.375,-0.265625,0.1796875,0.296875,0.5390625,0.671875,-0.71875,0.109375,0.203125,-0.078125,0.3515625,-0.4921875,-0.046875,0.1796875,0.25,0.359375,0.5234375,-0.6796875,-0.0078125,-0.15625,-0.09375,-0.46875,-0.1484375,-0.4765625,-0.3125,-0.5703125,-0.203125,0.234375,0.5859375,0.515625,-0.4296875,-0.453125,0.03125,0.578125,0.3515625,-0.1640625,-0.5390625,-0.640625,0.109375,-0.4453125,0.2265625,0.28125,0.2578125,-0.125,0.0859375,0.0390625,0.3515625,-0.2109375,0.265625,-0.046875,-0.0625,-0.1171875,0.34375,-0.2734375,0.0234375,0.328125,0.1015625,-0.0625,0.03125,-0.15625,0.4140625,0.0234375,0.015625,0.453125,0.421875,-0.59375,-0.359375,0.3828125,-0.296875,-0.859375,0.234375,-0.0625,0.40625,-