  ('Vitamin D is essential for calcium absorption and bone mineralisation. Target serum 25-hydroxyvitamin D level is > 50 nmol/L (sufficient) with optimal 75–150 nmol/L. Vitamin D deficiency (< 30 nmol/L) significantly impairs calcium absorption and increases fracture risk. Standard replacement: 1,000–2,000 IU/day; medical supervision required for ≥ 3,000 IU/day. Sunlight exposure (arms and legs, 10–15 min outside peak UV) remains the most efficient source.', '[0,0.2890625,0.1484375,-0.3671875,0,-0.0078125,0.1875,0.609375,0.1328125,-0.9453125,-0.6640625,-0.1015625,-0.1953125,0.5546875,0.6796875,-0.3359375,0.0390625,0.2421875,-0.1640625,0.046875,-0.296875,-0.0234375,-0.75,-0.421875,-0.65625,-0.0859375,0.03125,-0.0078125,0.3828125,0.390625,0.1953125,0.3671875,0.2421875,-0.2265625,-0.0703125,0.1328125,0.5859375,-0.046875,-0.6328125,-0.078125,-0.1796875,-0.421875,-0.0703125,0.5859375,-0.21875,-0.578125,-0.265625,-0.6171875,-0.1640625,0.046875,-0.2890625,0.0390625,0.265625,0.359375,-0.3203125,0.15625,0.5,0.2578125,-0.5078125,-0.4140625,0.109375,0.1015625,0.3046875,-0.296875,0.2265625,0.2109375,0.2421875,-0.0078125,0.0234375,-0.1953125,-0.578125,0.625,-0.1953125,-0.2890625,0.1015625,0.046875,-0.015625,0.1015625,-0.640625,0.5078125,0.1171875,0.1328125,-0.078125,0.5625,-0.3671875,0.25,-0.140625,0.203125,-0.421875,-0.140625,0.359375,-0.0625,-0.1953125,-0.21875,-0.46875,0.1171875,0.21875,0.0234375,0.3671875,-0.484375,0.359375,-0.1171875,-0.2890625,-0.046875,0.34375,0.0390625,-0.078125,0.5390625,-0.1875,0.5859375,-0.671875,-0.21875,-0.28125,0.1171875,-0.1328125,0.15625,0.2734375,-0.3828125,-0.546875,0.1953125,0.078125,0.1875,-0.2734375,0.0703125,-0.03125,-0.0703125,0.65625,0.125,-0.0859375,-0.203125,-0.359375,0.09375,-0.015625,-0.15625,0.0625,0,0.1015625,0.0234375,-0.2578125,0.2265625,-0.0390625,0.0546875,-0.28125,-0.2734375,-0.484375,0.109375,0.0703125,-0.265625,-0.25,0.015625,-0.0078125,-0.125,0.2578125,0.0546875,-0.1875,0.109375,0.109375,0.2421875,-0.1171875,0.1015625,-0.17