  ('Weight-bearing exercise is the most effective non-pharmacological intervention for building and maintaining bone density. High-impact loading (jogging, jumping, dancing) and resistance training improve bone mineral density in the spine and hip. RACGP 2024 recommends ≥ 2 strength training sessions/week and 150 minutes of moderate aerobic exercise/week for bone health. Balance training (tai chi, yoga) reduces falls risk by approximately 25%.', '[0,0.1171875,-0.4140625,-0.0859375,0,0.0390625,0.21875,0.6484375,0.078125,-0.90625,-0.46875,0.609375,-0.2265625,-0.46875,0.3828125,-0.3671875,0.09375,0.0078125,0.1875,-0.03125,-0.03125,-0.078125,-0.609375,-0.109375,-0.734375,0.265625,-0.0703125,-0.265625,-0.3828125,0.171875,-0.3203125,-0.1640625,-0.2265625,-0.1953125,-0.0078125,0.578125,0.0859375,-0.1015625,-0.203125,-0.1640625,-0.5,0.4140625,-0.03125,-0.1640625,-0.3046875,-0.375,0.0859375,-0.1328125,0.34375,0.4609375,-0.375,-0.3671875,0.296875,0.1484375,0.0234375,0.2109375,0.4140625,-0.03125,0.375,-0.1015625,-0.046875,-0.140625,0.078125,-0.1015625,0.171875,0.453125,-0.359375,-0.5625,0.0859375,0.2265625,0.2578125,0.40625,0.2421875,-0.6328125,0.421875,-0.09375,-0.1953125,0.15625,-0.5,0.0234375,-0.1484375,-0.2109375,-0.21875,0.78125,-0.0625,0.515625,-0.21875,0.0390625,-0.265625,0.4296875,0.2265625,-0.5,-0.296875,0.234375,0.171875,-0.234375,-0.46875,0.2109375,0.453125,0.0546875,0.1953125,-0.1171875,0.1015625,0.15625,0.40625,0,-0.46875,0.5078125,-0.4765625,0.5234375,-0.390625,-0.1171875,0.3984375,0.3359375,-0.0546875,-0.109375,-0.1796875,-0.1953125,-0.0703125,0.0078125,0.1875,-0.015625,0.1484375,0.03125,0.125,-0.1484375,-0.1171875,0.3125,-0.0546875,-0.0546875,0.2109375,-0.1796875,-0.1171875,0.21875,0.484375,0.0703125,-0.3984375,0.0546875,-0.1015625,0.0390625,0.0234375,0.2109375,-0.1953125,-0.1015625,0.0390625,-0.296875,-0.0625,0.1015625,-0.0859375,-0.1328125,0.0234375,0.0078125,-0.15625,0.25,-0.3984375,0.3125,0.1640625,0.3203125,-0.328125,-0.140625,-0.140625,-0.359375,-0.53125,