  ('BMI > 27.5 kg/m² is associated with a 4-fold increased risk of knee osteoarthritis (OA) compared to healthy weight (AIHW data). Each 5 kg increase in body weight increases knee joint load by 20 kg during walking. Weight loss of 5–10% in overweight individuals with knee OA reduces pain by 30–50% and improves function. Exercise therapy (aquatic and land-based) is first-line treatment for knee OA regardless of radiographic severity.', '[0,0.1015625,-0.609375,-0.25,0,0.0703125,-0.1015625,0.7265625,0.1640625,-0.984375,-0.3203125,0.3203125,0.1015625,-0.6796875,-0.2421875,-0.03125,0.09375,0.6171875,-0.0390625,0,0.1796875,0.046875,-0.484375,-0.25,-0.828125,0.125,-0.0625,0.0234375,-0.25,0.4453125,0.109375,0.1875,0.515625,-0.4453125,-0.046875,0.2109375,-0.265625,-0.0859375,-0.1484375,-0.3515625,-0.078125,0.1015625,0.203125,-0.1015625,-0.2421875,-0.3203125,0.3125,-0.2890625,-0.2578125,0.140625,-0.2578125,0.265625,-0.0859375,-0.0078125,0.2578125,-0.21875,0.8515625,-0.2734375,0.4765625,0.046875,0.3125,-0.2421875,0.5546875,0.3828125,0.0234375,0.015625,0.4765625,0.4140625,-0.1328125,0.03125,-0.6640625,-0.109375,0.3359375,0.1875,0.2265625,-0.4921875,-0.25,-0.0625,-0.796875,0.53125,-0.640625,0.125,-0.03125,0.7734375,-0.265625,-0.2734375,-0.4296875,-0.203125,0.1796875,-0.2421875,-0.1796875,-0.109375,-0.1171875,0.375,0.34375,-0.3515625,-0.03125,-0.1875,0.1484375,-0.09375,-0.1484375,-0.5234375,0.1171875,-0.1484375,0.5703125,0.140625,0.1953125,-0.296875,-0.3984375,-0.1796875,-0.46875,-0.2578125,0.2109375,0.1328125,-0.453125,0,-0.2578125,-0.15625,-0.359375,-0.2890625,0.421875,-0.203125,-0.0078125,0.2109375,0.09375,-0.109375,-0.234375,0.2578125,-0.4140625,0.1328125,-0.5,0.109375,0.2265625,-0.2734375,0.5234375,0.078125,-0.125,-0.15625,-0.359375,0.171875,0.4453125,-0.1875,0.140625,-0.0859375,-0.4140625,-0.671875,0.0546875,-0.390625,-0.1484375,-0.125,0.421875,-0.0703125,0.0078125,0.3046875,-0.109375,0.390625,0.25,0.1484375,0.1015625,0.265625,0,0.0703125,-0.796875,-0.515625,0.1015625,-0.1