  ('Rheumatoid arthritis (RA) is associated with systemic inflammation (elevated CRP, ESR, IL-6, TNF-α) and increased cardiovascular disease risk — 1.5–2x higher than age-matched controls. RA itself is a FRAX risk factor. Disease-modifying antirheumatic drugs (DMARDs) reduce systemic inflammation and fracture risk. Regular cardio-metabolic monitoring is recommended for RA patients.', '[0,0.7578125,-0.15625,-0.1953125,0,-0.2734375,-0.2421875,0.8828125,-0.09375,-0.9296875,-0.1796875,0.2890625,-0.0078125,-0.109375,0.7578125,-0.1484375,0.0078125,-0.5703125,-0.359375,-0.0625,-0.0703125,-0.5625,-0.828125,-0.5390625,-0.703125,0.265625,-0.0859375,0.0390625,0.015625,0.5390625,0,-0.1171875,0.734375,-0.2578125,-0.1796875,0.328125,-0.1484375,0.0078125,-0.5390625,0.21875,0.625,0.4921875,-0.09375,0.3359375,-0.65625,-0.4140625,0.4140625,0.3828125,0.1328125,-0.1875,0.2421875,-0.0703125,-0.015625,-0.1484375,0.2890625,-0.28125,0.2265625,-0.140625,0.421875,-0.1640625,0.5,0.0625,0.328125,0.5,-0.2421875,-0.140625,0.359375,0.1640625,0.03125,0.3359375,-0.40625,-0.0625,-0.3515625,0,-0.1171875,0.28125,-0.296875,0.53125,-0.34375,0.3984375,-0.6171875,-0.265625,0.21875,0.984375,-0.640625,0.0703125,0.2734375,-0.2109375,-0.265625,-0.203125,0.1484375,-0.0234375,-0.328125,0,0.2265625,-0.265625,0.1953125,-0.234375,0.1171875,-0.203125,-0.2734375,-0.140625,-0.59375,-0.1796875,0.5625,-0.296875,-0.34375,-0.3828125,0.234375,-0.3984375,-0.4296875,-0.25,-0.5078125,0.328125,-0.046875,-0.0625,0.296875,-0.4765625,0.140625,-0.65625,-0.2265625,-0.0546875,0,0.125,-0.6796875,0.3125,-0.109375,0.5234375,-0.2890625,-0.1953125,-0.6015625,-0.1328125,0.4921875,0.09375,-0.1953125,-0.109375,-0.3515625,0.171875,0.0703125,-0.2109375,-0.09375,-0.484375,-0.0625,0.0703125,0.046875,-0.4375,0.1796875,-0.125,0.1484375,0.203125,-0.0234375,0.0234375,-0.125,0.0625,-0.1171875,-0.1484375,0.1796875,-0.0546875,-0.015625,-0.3671875,0.0078125,0.0078125,-0.6015625,-0.78125,0.4375,-0.1484375,0.2578125,0.1171875,-0.421875,0.2734375,-0.5859