  ('Glucosamine sulfate (1,500 mg/day) and chondroitin sulfate (1,200 mg/day) have Level II evidence for symptomatic relief in knee osteoarthritis, particularly in moderate-to-severe OA. The GAIT trial (NEJM 2006) showed combination therapy superior to placebo in moderate-to-severe knee OA subgroup. Australian ARTG registered. Effect size is modest; response should be assessed at 3 months. No evidence for prevention of structural progression.', '[0,0.40625,-0.5234375,-0.2109375,0,-0.296875,0.5234375,0.5859375,0,-0.96875,-0.296875,0.390625,0.0703125,-0.2890625,0.6015625,0.0703125,0.1171875,0.328125,-0.171875,0.0234375,-0.2109375,-0.09375,-0.5859375,-0.546875,-0.5546875,-0.40625,0.03125,-0.1015625,-0.171875,-0.3046875,0.4375,-0.0625,0.671875,-0.3359375,0.03125,0.203125,-0.4453125,0.1875,-0.2734375,0.484375,0.375,-0.4296875,-0.375,0.046875,-0.3203125,0.578125,0.0390625,-0.2109375,-0.3671875,0.0078125,-0.3203125,0.1328125,0.1640625,0.15625,0.1171875,-0.03125,0.203125,-0.0078125,0.375,-0.578125,0.0703125,-0.1875,0.3515625,0.234375,0.1328125,0.5,-0.1015625,0.265625,-0.40625,-0.25,0.1875,0.265625,0.46875,0.03125,0.4765625,-0.4921875,-0.328125,-0.203125,-0.6015625,0.125,-0.265625,0.3515625,0.5,0.53125,-0.375,0.234375,-0.078125,-0.265625,0.046875,-0.5,-0.2734375,0.328125,0.296875,0.3671875,-0.265625,-0.171875,0.078125,-0.2890625,0.109375,-0.3984375,0.5,-0.21875,0.15625,-0.0234375,0.2578125,0.0703125,0.015625,-0.2421875,0.3515625,0.0625,-0.8046875,0.171875,-0.125,0.0390625,0.0625,0.375,0.3671875,-0.390625,0.1015625,-0.1328125,0.34375,-0.1328125,0.0625,-0.3984375,-0.390625,0.09375,0.453125,-0.0703125,-0.296875,0.09375,-0.609375,-0.1875,0.625,-0.1796875,0.359375,0.4921875,-0.0859375,-0.109375,-0.1796875,0.046875,-0.078125,-0.0859375,0.265625,-0.59375,-0.1875,-0.6171875,-0.453125,-0.59375,0.0390625,-0.0625,0.0625,-0.15625,-0.1875,0.234375,-0.578125,0.4140625,0.375,0.3515625,-0.0390625,-0.0625,-0.2265625,-0.0859375,-0.7109375,-0.8671875,-0.1875,-0.265625,0.1640625,-0.0234375,0.22