  ('Vitamin B12 (cobalamin) — NIH ODS: Deficiency threshold = serum B12 < 148 pmol/L (200 pg/mL). Optimal = > 300 pmol/L. Functional deficiency can occur with total B12 148–220 pmol/L — check holotranscobalamin (active B12) and methylmalonic acid for confirmation. Active B12 (holotranscobalamin) < 35 pmol/L indicates functional deficiency. Treatment: methylcobalamin 1,000 mcg/day orally. Risk groups: vegans, vegetarians, elderly, long-term metformin users.', '[0,0.1875,0.078125,-0.28125,0,0.046875,0.265625,0.421875,0.25,-0.9453125,-0.390625,-0.28125,-0.1875,0.5234375,0.1875,-0.328125,0.453125,-0.078125,-0.140625,0.0546875,-0.1953125,0.4140625,-0.484375,-0.7734375,-0.9375,0.578125,-0.1015625,-0.1015625,0.1875,0.3046875,0.2421875,0.125,0.6015625,0.2578125,-0.2890625,0.3046875,0.4296875,-0.140625,-0.703125,0.1484375,-0.1640625,-0.609375,-0.21875,0.4609375,-0.4921875,-0.234375,-0.0390625,-0.671875,0.0234375,0.0859375,-0.2734375,0.109375,0.34375,0.0078125,-0.6015625,0.2265625,0.5703125,0.1953125,-0.5078125,-0.609375,-0.0859375,-0.0234375,-0.1484375,-0.328125,0.4921875,-0.1171875,0.375,-0.1640625,-0.328125,0.4921875,-0.7109375,0.3359375,-0.2265625,0.375,0.734375,0.40625,-0.046875,-0.109375,-0.5,0.5078125,-0.0546875,0.4296875,0.3359375,0.7890625,-0.375,-0.015625,0.1171875,0.46875,-0.3515625,-0.515625,0.1484375,0.4453125,-0.40625,0.3203125,-0.171875,-0.5,0.078125,-0.2421875,0.21875,-0.546875,-0.2734375,-0.0390625,0.34375,-0.15625,0.6171875,0.15625,0.4609375,0.53125,0.125,-0.0078125,-0.609375,-0.015625,-0.2578125,-0.375,-0.359375,-0.375,0.4375,-0.5390625,-0.4765625,-0.3828125,0.046875,0.296875,-0.5078125,-0.1875,0.578125,0.390625,0.4375,-0.09375,-0.171875,-0.078125,-0.828125,0.0703125,0.359375,-0.09375,0.0078125,-0.1796875,0.4609375,0.5,0.4140625,0.3515625,0.203125,-0.1328125,0.125,-0.4140625,-0.046875,-0.421875,-0.0390625,0.109375,0.4453125,0.0234375,-0.34375,-0.2109375,0.3984375,0.0625,-0.3671875,0.4609375,-0.078125,-0.453125,0.140625,0.109375,-0.2109375,-0.359375,-0.78906