  ('Iron supplementation — WHO guidelines: Treat confirmed iron deficiency only (ferritin < 15 µg/L or < 30 µg/L with symptoms). Ferrous bisglycinate (chelated): 25–50 mg elemental iron, best tolerated form (superior GI profile vs ferrous sulfate). Take with 500 mg Vitamin C to enhance absorption by 2–3x. Separate from levothyroxine, quinolone antibiotics, calcium, magnesium by ≥ 2 hours. Recheck ferritin, haemoglobin after 3 months. Identify and treat underlying cause.', '[0,0.4140625,-0.265625,-0.21875,0,0.1796875,0.4140625,-0.203125,0.0234375,-0.921875,-0.2890625,0.0390625,0.265625,0.578125,0.734375,-0.3359375,-0.0703125,-0.5546875,-0.2421875,0.0234375,0.125,0.1875,-0.34375,-0.6796875,-0.6953125,-0.0703125,-0.0703125,-0.2734375,-0.2578125,-0.421875,-0.21875,-0.0859375,0.234375,-0.515625,-0.0625,0.1875,0.296875,0.1875,-0.4453125,-0.0546875,0,-0.359375,-0.2734375,0.1015625,-0.3984375,-0.2578125,0.2265625,0.3984375,0.015625,-0.0390625,-0.0859375,-0.046875,0.515625,0.3359375,-0.484375,0.0546875,0.6796875,0.3046875,-0.375,-0.7734375,0.421875,0.0625,0.5390625,-0.328125,0.328125,-0.0234375,-0.390625,0.5546875,-0.1171875,-0.203125,-0.484375,0.8359375,0.53125,0.265625,0.2734375,0.125,-0.2109375,-0.2421875,-0.7265625,0.5078125,-0.140625,0.0390625,0.234375,0.578125,-0.46875,-0.1171875,0.1640625,0.109375,-0.0625,-0.40625,-0.1328125,0.390625,-0.109375,0.421875,0.09375,0.125,-0.15625,-0.296875,-0.2734375,-0.7421875,0.359375,0.3125,0.1015625,0.46875,0.6328125,0.0859375,-0.1875,0.3359375,-0.03125,0.515625,-0.5703125,0.0390625,-0.2265625,0.0390625,0.2734375,-0.4296875,0.0859375,-0.6015625,0.1015625,-0.1015625,-0.0859375,-0.265625,-0.28125,-0.0390625,0.0546875,0.1796875,0.359375,-0.34375,0.2734375,-0.2578125,-0.1875,-0.03125,0.4296875,-0.453125,0.125,0.1796875,0.0859375,0.0390625,0.140625,-0.3203125,0.140625,-0.1796875,0.015625,-0.3203125,0.1484375,0.015625,0.2109375,-0.2421875,-0.3359375,-0.234375,-0.34375,-0.40625,-0.046875,-0.28125,-0.3984375,0.125,0.1875,-0.3984375,-0.203125,0