  ('NAD+ precursors (NMN/NR): Nicotinamide mononucleotide (NMN) and nicotinamide riboside (NR) raise cellular NAD+ levels, which decline with age. Published RCTs (2021–2024, Level II–III): NMN 250–500 mg/day increases blood NAD+; small trials show improved muscle function, insulin sensitivity, and walking speed in older adults. Long-term safety > 12 months not yet established in large trials. Promising but not yet Level I evidence. Phase III trials ongoing.', '[0,0.3515625,-0.1953125,-0.25,0,0.140625,0.375,0.5546875,-0.0625,-0.9140625,-0.4140625,-0.2109375,0,-0.0703125,0.46875,-0.1875,-0.125,-0.5625,-0.1953125,0,-0.0625,0.0234375,-0.234375,-0.5078125,-0.8515625,-0.421875,-0.21875,0.09375,-0.4609375,0.3515625,-0.15625,0.0078125,0.765625,0.0546875,0.203125,0.375,-0.1875,0.015625,-0.234375,0.1640625,0.4453125,-0.1875,0.4140625,0.234375,0.1484375,0.6015625,0.1484375,-0.1640625,0.6328125,0.3125,0.171875,-0.34375,0.1328125,-0.25,-0.578125,0.6171875,0.03125,-0.1171875,-0.265625,-0.546875,0.1015625,0.625,0.5,0.1953125,0.0859375,0.078125,0.2578125,-0.3984375,-0.125,-0.4453125,-0.3515625,0.53125,-0.03125,0.2109375,0.359375,-0.1328125,0.3046875,-0.171875,-0.3515625,0.3984375,0.09375,0.140625,-0.28125,0.765625,-0.1171875,0.53125,0.0390625,0.015625,0.0625,0.75,0.0078125,-0.09375,0.171875,-0.3125,0.1953125,-0.2421875,0.109375,-0.046875,0.4140625,-0.5859375,0.5234375,0.1796875,0.4921875,0.078125,0.1875,0.1640625,0.25,-0.359375,0.078125,0.2421875,-0.3125,0.140625,0.2421875,0.53125,-0.3359375,0,0.40625,-0.3203125,0.2265625,-0.328125,0.0625,0.0703125,-0.3828125,-0.1640625,0.1953125,-0.3203125,-0.3359375,0.203125,0.0078125,0.0625,-0.171875,0.078125,0.09375,0.0625,0.046875,0.2421875,-0.1640625,0.3515625,-0.109375,0.0859375,-0.0234375,0.2109375,0.2265625,0.078125,0.2265625,0.265625,-0.0703125,-0.078125,0.375,-0.03125,0.296875,-0.171875,0.0625,0.109375,0.0390625,-0.0234375,-0.0546875,0.1953125,-0.0390625,-0.3984375,0.015625,0.3984375,-0.4765625,-0.5234375,-0.03125,-0.09375,0.0234375,0.03