  ('Anticoagulant interactions with supplements: Fish oil > 3 g/day, Vitamin E > 400 IU/day, CoQ10, and Ginkgo biloba each independently increase bleeding risk when combined with anticoagulants (warfarin, rivaroxaban, apixaban, dabigatran). Fish oil inhibits platelet aggregation via TXA2 reduction. Vitamin E inhibits platelet aggregation and Vitamin K-dependent coagulation factors. These combinations should be reviewed by a prescribing doctor. Supplement regimens must be disclosed to anticoagulant-prescribing clinicians.', '[0,-0.03125,-0.15625,-0.484375,0,-0.2578125,0.125,0.7109375,0.109375,-0.9765625,-0.09375,0.5234375,0.2109375,-0.03125,0.375,-0.2421875,0.21875,-0.59375,0.390625,0.0234375,-0.1875,-0.0390625,-0.8046875,-0.484375,-0.765625,0.1796875,0.046875,0.0859375,-0.2109375,0.3125,-0.2890625,-0.09375,0.4296875,0.0625,-0.21875,0.578125,-0.390625,0.0234375,-0.578125,-0.0546875,0.4375,-0.234375,-0.0625,0.4296875,0.109375,-0.015625,0.359375,0.0234375,0.296875,0.0234375,0.0859375,0.15625,0.1796875,0,0.375,0.4609375,0.4453125,-0.28125,-0.5,-0.5390625,-0.015625,-0.234375,0.140625,-0.5625,0.0859375,-0.1484375,0.5078125,0.203125,-0.0390625,-0.125,-0.4375,0.625,0.5234375,0.1953125,0.21875,-0.015625,-0.046875,0,-0.1484375,0.4375,-0.4140625,-0.3125,0.21875,0.3984375,0.296875,0.0078125,0.15625,0.015625,0.34375,-0.125,0.0625,0.1328125,0.0234375,0.21875,-0.375,-0.09375,-0.21875,0.109375,0.0078125,0.328125,0.140625,0.2109375,-0.375,-0.2578125,0.1328125,0.390625,-0.015625,-0.1640625,-0.1171875,0.5625,-0.6015625,0.375,-0.71875,0.3515625,-0.34375,-0.296875,0.171875,-0.6875,-0.171875,-0.4921875,-0.0546875,-0.1875,-0.1953125,0.078125,-0.203125,-0.1328125,0.09375,0.1875,0.171875,0.125,-0.109375,-0.0546875,0.625,-0.3671875,-0.1875,0.28125,-0.2265625,0.046875,0.4140625,-0.0234375,-0.3125,-0.09375,-0.328125,-0.1015625,-0.0859375,-0.03125,-0.1171875,-0.4296875,0.0234375,0.1015625,0.078125,-0.34375,0.21875,0.140625,-0.390625,0.140625,0.2265625,0.4296875,-0.125,-0.421875,0.1328125,0.0156