  ('St John''s Wort (Hypericum perforatum) is a potent inducer of CYP3A4 (metabolic enzyme) and P-glycoprotein (drug efflux pump). Clinical consequences: reduces plasma concentrations of oral contraceptives (breakthrough bleeding, contraceptive failure), SSRIs/SNRIs (reduced efficacy; potential serotonin syndrome), warfarin (reduced anticoagulation, INR drop, thromboembolism risk), digoxin, HIV antiretrovirals, cyclosporin (organ rejection risk), and statins. ABSOLUTE CONTRAINDICATION with antidepressants, OCP, warfarin, and immunosuppressants.', '[0,0.5625,0.1953125,-0.375,0,-0.7578125,0.25,0.390625,0.0234375,-0.9921875,0.1484375,0.4375,0.1015625,0.40625,0.421875,-0.21875,0.328125,-0.453125,-0.3125,-0.0390625,-0.1015625,0.0546875,-0.71875,-0.5390625,-0.21875,0.1640625,-0.09375,0.0546875,0.015625,-0.09375,0.078125,0.03125,0.234375,-0.2578125,-0.0078125,0.1796875,-0.328125,-0.2265625,-0.2109375,0.515625,0.15625,-0.265625,0.15625,0.2890625,0.1796875,0.1875,0.3125,0.125,0.359375,-0.015625,-0.1953125,0.078125,0.265625,0.1484375,-0.0234375,0.1640625,0.09375,-0.09375,0.015625,-0.640625,0.4296875,0.140625,-0.265625,-0.03125,0.171875,0.0234375,0.15625,0.1796875,-0.328125,-0.1484375,0.1953125,0.28125,-0.046875,-0.4375,0.1640625,-0.0078125,-0.140625,-0.2421875,0.1953125,0.515625,-0.09375,0.2578125,0.3125,0.7734375,-0.0703125,0.5078125,0.453125,-0.109375,-0.3125,-0.4296875,-0.265625,0.3671875,0.1328125,-0.125,0.2109375,-0.0546875,0.328125,-0.265625,0.0703125,0.234375,0.1796875,0.390625,-0.109375,0.015625,-0.2578125,-0.078125,-0.359375,-0.0078125,0.125,0.359375,-0.0390625,0.1953125,0.328125,0.3046875,0.2734375,-0.046875,-0.28125,-0.0078125,0.015625,-0.390625,-0.2578125,-0.3359375,0.1328125,-0.359375,0.015625,-0.0703125,-0.0859375,0.1328125,0.0625,-0.171875,0.171875,-0.203125,0.484375,-0.390625,0.1953125,0.125,0.1953125,0.09375,-0.0546875,-0.15625,0.0234375,-0.3125,-0.0859375,0.1953125,-0.0546875,0.03125,0.1484375,-0.328125,0.1015625,-0.078125,-0.2109375,-0.0546875,0.359375,0.13