  ('Calcium and iron compete for absorption via the divalent metal transporter-1 (DMT1) in the duodenum. Calcium (≥ 300 mg) co-administered with iron reduces non-haem iron absorption by 30–60%. This interaction is clinically significant in iron-deficiency anaemia management. Recommendation: take iron ≥ 2 hours apart from calcium supplements or dairy-rich meals.', '[0,0.3828125,-0.2578125,-0.0859375,0,0.4453125,-0.1484375,0.3515625,0.03125,-0.90625,-0.3046875,0.234375,0.0859375,-0.0625,0.609375,-0.5859375,-0.2265625,-0.5390625,0.328125,0.0546875,-0.046875,0.28125,-0.265625,-0.78125,-0.5859375,-0.140625,-0.0390625,-0.5,-0.390625,0.109375,0.34375,-0.0078125,0,-0.21875,-0.203125,0.2734375,0.625,-0.046875,-0.2578125,-0.328125,-0.5703125,-0.328125,0.296875,0.140625,-0.1484375,-0.2734375,0.421875,0.1796875,0.1953125,0.0625,-0.4375,-0.0625,0.40625,-0.015625,-0.6953125,-0.0703125,0.1015625,0.1328125,-0.359375,-0.546875,-0.1484375,-0.515625,0.7421875,-0.03125,0.234375,0.25,0.0078125,0.796875,-0.5078125,0.3984375,-0.3203125,-0.109375,0.3125,0.328125,-0.1796875,0.5078125,0.0859375,0.21875,0.03125,0.2734375,-0.2109375,-0.1640625,-0.15625,0.8203125,-0.375,-0.4296875,-0.0234375,-0.421875,0.09375,0.0234375,-0.015625,0.1640625,-0.015625,0.6328125,-0.1484375,0.25,0.421875,0.2109375,-0.5703125,-0.4375,0.359375,0.578125,0.109375,0.8515625,0.15625,-0.0390625,-0.234375,0.421875,0.2890625,0.15625,-0.6015625,-0.0390625,0.265625,0.2109375,0.4375,0.0859375,0.0390625,-0.28125,0.1640625,0.1328125,-0.34375,0.375,-0.203125,-0.25,0.140625,-0.3046875,0.2421875,0.21875,0.5859375,-0.6953125,-0.1953125,0.0234375,0.453125,0.0078125,0.1953125,-0.109375,0.09375,0.1640625,0,-0.3671875,0.078125,-0.03125,-0.0625,-0.6171875,-0.0703125,0.0703125,-0.125,-0.25,-0.3359375,0.2421875,-0.171875,-0.296875,-0.15625,-0.40625,0.1796875,-0.1171875,0.0703125,-0.4296875,-0.328125,-0.1640625,0.0625,-0.0078125,-0.7578125,-0.7734375,-0.4296875,0.40625,0.203125,0.3359375,-0.3203125,-0.4296875,0.0625,-0.0078125,0.2890625,0.05