  ('Vitamin E (alpha-tocopherol) > 400 IU/day has antiplatelet effects and may increase bleeding risk, particularly in the perioperative period or when combined with anticoagulants or antiplatelet drugs (aspirin, clopidogrel). The HOPE-TOO trial (2005) found that long-term Vitamin E supplementation (400 IU/day) increased risk of heart failure in high-risk patients. Advise discontinuation ≥ 7 days before elective surgery.', '[0,0.1875,0.203125,-0.6328125,0,-0.046875,0.375,0.75,0.125,-0.9765625,-0.1640625,0.1796875,0.171875,0.2265625,0.15625,-0.3125,-0.1484375,-0.4765625,0.28125,-0.03125,0.1171875,0.1015625,-0.6015625,-0.5234375,-0.640625,0.203125,0.0390625,-0.1640625,0.1875,0.421875,-0.3046875,-0.1875,0.703125,0.09375,-0.109375,0.1875,-0.25,-0.0859375,-0.5390625,0.484375,-0.046875,-0.34375,-0.1953125,0.515625,-0.4453125,-0.0703125,0.2109375,-0.3125,0.4765625,-0.2734375,-0.0234375,0.25,0.296875,-0.21875,0.0859375,0.4140625,0.09375,-0.140625,-0.421875,-0.5078125,0.09375,-0.5859375,0.015625,-0.3828125,-0.1328125,0.1484375,0.3671875,-0.4296875,-0.125,-0.6484375,-0.5078125,0.4296875,0.1953125,-0.3515625,0.3203125,0.5390625,0.125,-0.1484375,-0.375,-0.0078125,-0.1171875,-0.4140625,0.28125,0.7265625,0.1484375,-0.21875,0.1171875,-0.0390625,0.3046875,-0.5,0.1328125,-0.0390625,-0.1796875,-0.265625,-0.484375,-0.0859375,-0.46875,-0.40625,-0.4609375,0.0078125,0.140625,-0.140625,-0.625,-0.09375,-0.046875,-0.015625,-0.3515625,0.0546875,-0.078125,0.5234375,-0.6953125,0.4453125,-0.4765625,0.3515625,-0.171875,-0.5,0.1640625,-0.6015625,-0.2109375,-0.2109375,-0.1171875,0.15625,-0.4921875,0.390625,-0.1171875,0.1875,0.2734375,0.1328125,-0.015625,0.5,-0.59375,-0.03125,0.4296875,-0.2578125,-0.0078125,-0.09375,0.265625,-0.1640625,0.2890625,0.265625,0.0703125,-0.1171875,-0.2265625,-0.1484375,-0.1640625,-0.328125,-0.2578125,0.015625,-0.1953125,0.140625,0.15625,-0.109375,-0.0078125,0.03125,-0.1953125,0.171875,0.1875,0.3125,-0.0234375,-0.1015625,0.1484375,0.171875,-0.234375,-0.5625,-0.125,-0.0078